  <answer><![CDATA[<p>You can pay your final balance through the ‘manage my booking’ page. You will need your booking reference, lead passenger surname and departure date to log in: <span><a href="https://my.inghams.co.uk/login">https://my.inghams.co.uk/login</a></span> or you can call our payments team on 01483 791961.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>If you have booked through a travel agent, please contact them directly to make payment.</p>]]></answer>
